  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. To convert degrees to radians, multiply by &pi;/180. So 45&deg; = 45 &middot; (&pi;/180) = &pi;/4 radians. Choice B is half the correct value. Choice C corresponds to 90&deg;. Choice D corresponds to 180&deg;.</p>",
